item.title: Features
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: [one_half last="no" animation_type="none" animation_direction="down" animation_speed=""][tdp_video title="" type="url" url="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VgYK3jIiiWE" poster="{{}}" embed="" color=""][/one_half] [one_half last="yes" animation_type="none" animation_direction="down" animation_speed=""] [spacer space="50px"] [heading type="line" title="Automatic Theme Installation" subtitle="" icon="flash"] If you are new to WordPress or have problems creating posts or pages that look like the theme preview you can import dummy demo data posts and pages here that will definitely help to understand how those tasks are done. The automatic installer will also setup the homepage for you and import some demo vehicles. Note that images aren't included in the package. [/one_half] [spacer space="80px"] [one_half last="no" animation_type="none" animation_direction="down" animation_speed=""] [heading type="line" title="WooCommerce Support" subtitle="" icon="thumbs-up-alt"] AutoDealer is the only professional WordPress theme that provides a full frontend submission system and a package system powered by WooCommerce. Through the use of WooCommerce you can use specific products as packages that your users can buy to submit vehicles on your website. Nonetheless the WooCommerce integration allows you to use any kind of payment gateway! [/one_half] [one_half last="yes" animation_type="none" animation_direction="down" animation_speed=""][spacer space="40px"][/one_half] [spacer space="80px"] [one_half last="no" animation_type="none" animation_direction="down" animation_speed=""][/one_half] [one_half last="yes" animation_type="none" animation_direction="down" animation_speed=""] [heading type="line" title="Front-End Profiles & Dealer Profiles" subtitle="" icon="users-1"] The AutoDealer theme provides an exclusive front-end profile management page, users will be able to register and customize their profiles from the front-end without having to access to your WP Dashboard. Users can also register themselves as "dealers", if a user is registered as a dealer he will gain access to exclusive custom profile fields that allow him to customize his business details, other than this, their listings pages will show an exclusive widget and also have their own profile pages with business details. [/one_half] [spacer space="80px"] [one_half last="no" animation_type="none" animation_direction="down" animation_speed=""] [spacer space="50px"] [heading type="line" title="Set Listings To Expire" subtitle="" icon="users-1"] Listings can expire after a certain period of time, set the amount of days through the theme options panel, or if needed you can also set a different expiration time for each package that you create, giving you more flexibility on your payment plans and features. [/one_half] [one_half last="yes" animation_type="none" animation_direction="down" animation_speed=""][/one_half] [spacer space="80px"] [one_third last="no"][tdp_iconbox image="flag" title="100% Translatable" type="standard-title" animation="none" animation_delay="200" icon_color="#8224e3"]Theme can be translated through the integrated localization files .mo and .po files[/tdp_iconbox][/one_third] [one_third last="no"][tdp_iconbox image="th-list" title="MegaMenu" type="standard-title" animation="none" animation_delay="200" icon_color="#8224e3"]Theme comes with integrated support for megamenu no need for a plugin.[/tdp_iconbox][/one_third] [one_third last="yes"][tdp_iconbox image="mobile" title="Responsive Theme" type="standard-title" animation="none" animation_delay="200" icon_color="#8224e3"]The theme adapts to the viewport of each different screen resolution and mobile devices.[/tdp_iconbox][/one_third] [spacer space="50px"] [one_third last="no"][tdp_iconbox image="leaf" title="Retina Ready" type="standard-title" animation="none" animation_delay="200" icon_color="#8224e3"]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit.
